### Search partner categories - by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/search?name=manufact

### Search partner categories - by name, active only (default)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/search?name=market&active=true

### Search partner categories - by name, including inactive
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/search?name=market&active=false

### Search partner categories - no results
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/search?name=nonexistent